column5: Take 3 lbs of pickerel, 2lbs of taters, homemade tartar sauce and some Cajun coating. What do you got???  A little taste of heaven. Me and the boys are living high.
hmmm, my walleye don't come with that kit.
Man here  thought this post was about the zero gravity Kate Upton photo shoot...Lol Seriously thou nice catch..
I'm suddenly hungry again   Enjoy that treat Bruce
